Now open `.gitignore` in any text editor and make sure it contains:
```
# Environment & secrets
.env

# Python virtual environment
venv/
.venv/
env/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Database (optional — remove this line if you want to keep db in repo)
data/
*.db

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log